-- Signature Group Names Bouchard CEO After Proxy Fight Settled
-- B y   S o n j a   E l m q u i s t
-- 2013-06-05T13:01:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-05/signature-group-names-bouchard-ceo-after-proxy-fight-settled.html
Signature Group Holdings Inc., an
investment company, named Craig Bouchard as chairman and chief
executive officer after settling a proxy fight.  Signature plans to issue shares to fund “large
acquisitions,” it said in a statement today.  Bouchard was among investors who said  Sherman Oaks ,
California-based Signature wasn’t generating a sufficient
shareholder value.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonja Elmquist in New York at 
